messages.content: Rodophis’ mindscape is cold and icy, with lots of icicles and things that look like glass. There is a small village of igloos.

As Dulci entered Rodos mindscape everything seemed to gain a pastel color along with multiple sweets popping up on the igloos. Kinda making them look like gingerbread houses. "Huh....This must be Rodos mindscape...."
Rodophis looked around in surprise. “Oh...this is something else...” she said quietly.
She flew into the air a bit to try and find Rodo. Once seeing her she landed in front of her "Hi babe!"
"Oh! Uh...hey there!" She waved at her. "I take it this is your handiwork?"
She looked around and nodded "Yup! Seems like it!"
"I...I like it, it meshes well."
"Oh thank you! You have a very lovely mindscape."
"You...think so?" She blushed a bit.
She nodded
“Aww...thanks.” She kissed her.
She happily kissed back!
Her tail wagged, kicking up a little bit of snow.
She noticed and smiled, deciding to dip her in the kiss
She laughed, but then she had a weird idea.
She smiled "I love you~"
"Oh, I love you too..."
She kept close to her.
She held her hand, smiling at her
She purred at her, nuzzling her neck.
She blushed a bit and purred back
“God, you’re so cute...”
"So are you!!!"
She just blushed in response.
Her tail wagged happily
“...You know, though, I just had an idea...”
She tilted her head
“...What if we fell asleep *in here*?”
"Huh....That would be interesting...."
“...You wanna try?”
"Sure!"
She gave a quick nod, smiling. “Thanks.”
She gave her a smooch
She kissed her back, before laying down and falling asleep.
She fell asleep with her soon after
....Another Rodophis appears. “This doesn’t look that different...”
Another Dulci appears as well
“...Hmmm...” she looked around.
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
"How odd...."
“I thought we’d be in another mindsca- Wait, what’s that?” She pointed at two figures.
"I....i think....thats us....?"
“So...there’s two of us now?”
She nodded
“....so if we fell asleep a bunch of times, there’d be a bunch of us?”
"I dont know....."
“I don’t either, but...let’s maybe not try that.” Rodophis sits next to her other self.
She nodded "yeah.."
“C’mon, sit with me.”
She sat next to her
“Ain’t that something...?” She asked, looking down at her other self.
"So odd...."
“I know, I thought we would go into another mindscape or something.”
She nodded "Yeah..."
“But when you think about it, we are kind of...inception here.”
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
"Yeah...we are...."
“...Now I’m curious.” She stroked the cheek of the sleeping Dulci.
The Awake Ducli feels that
She looked up at her. “Did you...?”
She nodded
“...Holy cow.”
She poked the sleeping Rodos cheek
“Hey!” The awake Rodophis held onto her cheek.
She giggled
She started tickling asleep Dulci.
"Yeep!" She starts giggling "H-Hey!"
“That’s what you get!”
(@Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
She tackled Rodo in a hug, giggling still
She started laughing as well.
She gave her a smooch
She kissed her back.
"Mmm I love you so much~"
“I love you too...awake and asleep.”
She picks her up and goes over ti a deeper snow pile and drops her in it, giggling
“Woah!” She yelps as she gets knocked down.
She sticks her tounge out at her
She gave off a playful growl.
She giggled and ran off "CATCH ME IF YOU CAN~!!"
She pounced and ran after her on all fours.
Dulci was suprised and kept running
She kept behind her, gaining.
She began to fly
She tried jumping up and down.
She stuck her tounge out at her
“You’re not getting away that easy!!”
She flew up higher
“...Well then.”
She tried jumping up to reach her, but she landed flat on her face.
Then, an idea hit her. She ran over to asleep Dulci and pushed down on her back.
And she fell "EEP!"
“YEAH!” She cheered.
"Ow....." She mumbled as she got up
“Oh, uh...” she approached her. “Sorry...”
She threw a snowball at her, giggling "Im fine! Just landed in a weird way!"
“Woah!” She stumbled back, sighing in relief.
She tackled her in a hug, giggling "I love you~"
She smiled, purring at her. “You too~”
She smooches her!!!
She quickly kissed her back. “...Hey, want some cocoa?”
"Yeah!!!"
She helped up her sleeping self. “Follow me, then, there’s some in an igloo.”
Dulci helped up her sleeping self as well "Ok!"
She smiled at her, leading her to the igloo where the cocoa was.
Dulci followed after her
The igloo was nice and cozy, with four chairs that look to be made for camping. The cocoa was on a bar of ice, with cups next to it.
"Ooo......How lovely!!!" She smiled
“You like it? I know it’s not much, but...Y’know, ice.”
She nodded with a smile "Its nice and cozy!!"
“Aww...” she blushed, setting her sleeping self in a chair.
Dulci did the same, humming softlt
She poured some cocoa into the cups. “Want marshmallows?”
She nodded "Yes please!!!!"
“OK...” she pulled out a small bowl and put the marshmallows in the cup. “Great thing about having hot chocolate in your mind is you never run out of cocoa or marshmallows.”
She giggled "Your right~"
She gave one to her, before glancing at their sleeping selves. “Wonder how we wake them up...”
"Hm...maybe a pinch....?" She hummed
“That could work...so we both pinch ourselves?”
"Orrrr we can make it more fun and I pinch you~" she giggled
“Uhhh...cooould work?”
She reached over to pinch the sleeping Rodo
The sleeping Rodo woke up pretty quickly. “Ow!”
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
(Oh shit thanks)
Dulci giggled, wings fluttering a bit
(Should they both be awake??)
(Uhhhh yeah
“Ow, Ow, Ow...” both of them said together, before Rodophis pinched the sleeping Dulci.
Dulci yelped and the sleeping Dulci woke up
“Morning~” she laughed, giving her a kiss.
She giggled and kissed back "Morning my love~"
The other Rodophis stifled back a stunned laugh. "Wow..."
"Oh seems like there can be 2 of us at any given time!" Du2i hummed
"Hey, that's pretty cool!" Ro2 said, smiling.
Dul2i nodded humming
"...God, can you imagine a whole little *village* of us?"
"I dont think I wanna know." She hummed
"Just a thought..."
"Oh!" Rodo perked up. "Do you guys want cocoa too?" She asked the other pair.
Ro2 thought for a second. "...Maybe?"
"Hmmm sure!!!" Dul2i grinned
"OK, then." Rodophis smiled. "You want marshmallows too?"
Both Dulcis answered with YES
"Well, OK then!" Rodophis looked a little intimidated, while Ro2 laughed.
Dulci giggled "Wow what perfect sync"
"I'll say." Ro2 said, wrapping an arm around Dul2.
Rodophis comes back, giving both Dulcis their cocoa.
Both their tails wag
She gives one to her other self, before sitting down with her own. Both of their tails curled around their girlfriends.

“This is weird...”
“Yeah, I know.”
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
They are happily drinking their hot coco
The rodos start drinking as well.
Dul2i is humming a bit
Ro2 humms along with her.
Shes humming a _certain song_
Her ears perked up when she recognized the song and she chuckled.
Dulci starts to sing it!
Rodo isn’t sure of the lyrics so she just humms along.
What a lovely singing voice
“You...sound great...” Ro2 smiled.
"Thanks~" Dul2i responded fir Dulci

“I could listen to you sing all day and night...”
Ro2 nodded in agreement.
Both blushed at that
“Well, it’s true!”
"Thanks..." Dulci played with her hair a bit
She stroked her hair, drinking a little more cocoa.
She purred a bit
Both Rodos purred back.
Dulci hugged Rodo ans kissed her cheek
Rodo kisses her back, while Ro2 watches.
Dul2i lays her head on Ro2s lap
“So cute...”
Bith Dulcis are purring loudly

“God, we’re lucky, aren’t we?”
“Yeah...”
They are content on their gfs
“I love you, sweetie...” Ro2 said, which got a surprised look from Rodo.

"Mmmm I love you too my little Blueberry~" Dul2i giggled

Dulci blinked at that
“Well...that’s a nice one.”
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
(Sowwy was desgining feral Vulpe
(Ah)
"Its cute....." Dulci hummed
“You th-think so?”
Dulci nodded

“I...might start using that.”
“Nice.” Ro2 grinned.

Dul2i, being ALOT more confident then Dulci, decides to kiss Ro2s neck and gently bite. 

Dulci saw that and squeaked

Rodo felt her neck, surprised. 
Ro2 let out a deep, oddly seductive growl.

Dulci covered her face with her hands, completely embarrassed by what the other her was doing

Dul2i giggled "My oh my~ Thats new~" She said before going back to leaving marks
Rodophis stared in shock as Ro2 caressed Dul2i.
Dulcis face is as red as her hair and her wings are fluttering alot

“What...what is this...?!”
“Simple. Your desires.”
"W-w-well.....I-Its true I-Ive always d-dreamed of th-this.......M-mainly m-me teasing yo-you Rodo....." Dulci mumbled
“And...well...I’ve always wanted to be less awkward...” Rodo nodded.
"......Do....you wanna go to my mindscape.....Its....got a bed......and uh....." Dulci couldn't finish her sentence
“...Can...Can we *all* go?”
"Yeah.....Why not...."

“Sounds good.”
“A-All right, lets...let’s do it...”
Dulci closed her eyes and they probably shifted to #dulci
Rodophis’ mindscape has become a blizzard, trying to freeze the goop.
Its still trying to crawl all over and envelop Rodo
“S-Stay...back...” she snarled, trying to pull herself free.
She can hear whispers telling her to give in
“N-No, not if there’s a chance...I can keep Dulci safe...”
The whispers keep up
The blizzard becomes more intense.
"_Give in and we can make you stronger~_" One of the whispers said
“No! No, I’m plenty strong on my own!”!
"_We can help you protect Dulci..._" Its trying to use any memories it has access to, to get her to give in
“W-Why should I trust you?!”
"_just become one....youll feel so good~_"
She tries to fight back, but she’s feeling weaker. “I-I don’t...need you...”
"_Just give in~ You wont need to worry about anything~_"
“Promise...you won’t...hurt Dulci....?”
"_Promise~_" Its the half truth
Rodophis tried to fight back one last time, but her knees buckled and she fell flat on her face.
The goop toom control, making sure Rodo wouldn't wake up very easily
